mb.ernet.in |date= |accessdate=2012-07-11}}</ref>\n\n==Career==\n===Academic positions===\nHe joined [[IIMB]] as an [[assistant professor]] in 1986. He is currently a senior [[Professor]] in the area of Finance and Control. He is a [[Visiting Fellow]] at [[Manchester Business School]], [[United Kingdom]] and a [[Visiting Professor]] at [[Osaka University]], [[Japan]].\n\n==Books==\nHe has authored the following books which are part of the syllabus in many renowned B-schools.\n* Financial Accounting: A Managerial Perspective, (Sixth Edition, 2017) PHI Learning Private Limited, Delhi, eBook and pBook available at www.phindia.com <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.phindia.com/Books/BookDetail/OTc4ODEyMDM1MzQzNQ |title=Financial Accounting : A Managerial Perspective By: Narayanaswamy, R |publisher=Phindia.com |date=2014-03-01 |accessdate=2012-07-11}}</ref>\n* Financial Reporting Asia Pacific: Financial Reporting in India, CCH Asia Pte Limited, Singapore\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Narayanaswamy, R.}}\n[[Category:Indian academics]]\n[[Category:Indian Institute of Management Bangalore faculty]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Year of birth missing (living people)]]\n", "text_old": "{{Multiple issues|\n{{Advert|date=November 2018}}\n{{BLP sources|date=July 2012}}\n}}\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2018}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=May 2018}}\n\n{{Infobox person\n| name           = R. Narayanaswamy <br> \u0bb0\u0bbe \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0baf\u0ba3\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bbf\n| image          =\n| birth_date     = 1956 or 1957<ref>{{cite web|last=Ghosh |first=Ahona |url=http://archives.digitaltoday.in/businesstoday/20060716/cover5.html |title=Business Today |publisher=Archives.digitaltoday.in |date=2006-07-16 |accessdate=2012-07-11}}</ref>\n| birth_place    = \n| nationality    =\n| occupation     = [[Professor]]\n| alma_mater     = [[University of Madras]]<br>[[University of New South Wales]]<br>[[Institute of Chartered Accountants of Ind